# OOHAPP

OOHAPP is an outdoor advertising technology platform that helps brands, agencies, and businesses discover, compare, and book billboard and hoarding advertising spaces across India.

Founded in 2022, OOHAPP simplifies outdoor advertising by combining technology with strategic media placement. The platform enables advertisers to access multiple outdoor advertising locations, evaluate pricing, and execute impactful advertising campaigns.

